  <div class="row">
    <h1>How much does EZ Golf League cost?</h1>
    <p class="lead">Using EZ Golf League is the best way to make sure all of your league operations run smoothly.</p>
    <p class="lead">Save <mark>hours per month</mark> that you previously spent with spreadsheets or inferior software. Plus, your golfers will <mark>love</mark> the quick access to scores and standings!</p>
  </div>

