    <div class="col-md-2">&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h2>Common Questions</h2>
      <div class="text-left">
        <p><strong>Do you have smartphone apps?</strong></p>
        <p>Yes, we have apps for both iOS and Android available in the App Store and Google Play.</p>

        <p><strong>What features can I use from my phone?</strong></p>
        <p>Our apps allow you to score tournaments and view your standings. On iOS, you're also able to register for upcoming tournaments - coming soon on Android.</p>

        <p><strong>I've got a lot of golfers in my league but many of them don't play each year. Will I have to pay for them?</strong></p>
        <p>You are only billed for 'active' golfers, i.e. those that participate in tournaments. You can change which golfers are active at any time.</p>

        <p><strong>I have 13 golfers in my league. Do I need to pay for all 13 golfers or are the first 12 free?</strong></p>
        <p>You'd pay for 13 golfers. Our free trial is for leagues with 12 or fewer golfers. Paid plans need to cover all golfers active in the league.</p>

        <p><strong>How am I billed?</strong></p>
        <p>Via credit card. We accept Visa, Mastercard and American Express.</p>

        <p><strong>Can I add active golfers later if I need to?</strong></p>
        <p>Yes, absolutely. If you need to add more golfers, the system will provide you with an updated balance.</p>

        <p><strong>What is your refund policy?</strong></p>
        <p>We don't offer refunds. We encourage you to try our free trial before signing up to get a feel for how the system works.</p>

        <p><strong>Which game types do you support?</strong></p>
        <p>We currently support stroke play, match play, scramble, shamble, stableford, best ball and various team configurations. If you have a question about a specific game type used in your league, contact us at <a href='mailto:support@ezgolfleague.com?subject=Game%20Type%20Question'>support@ezgolfleague.com</a>. We are adding game types all the time and would love to hear from you!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2">&nbsp;</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Billing Calculator</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>An 'active golfer' is one that plays in tournaments.</p>
        <p>A 'season' includes a certain number of tournaments. Typically a season is a year but it can be any length.</p>

        <table class="table table-striped">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Number of Active Golfers</td>
              <td><input type="number" name="active_golfers" value="15" id="active_golfers"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Number of Tournaments Per Season</td>
              <td><input type="number" name="tournaments_per_season" value="10" id="tournaments_per_season"></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Total Cost</strong> <span id="cost_details"></span></td>
              <td id="total_cost">XX</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Continue</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  $("#active_golfers").keyup(function() {
    updateCalculatedCost();
  });

  $("#tournaments_per_season").keyup(function() {
    updateCalculatedCost();
  });

  $("#active_golfers").change(function() {
    updateCalculatedCost();
  });

  $("#tournaments_per_season").change(function() {
    updateCalculatedCost();
  });

  function updateCalculatedCost() {
    var golfers = $("#active_golfers").val();
    var tournaments = $("#tournaments_per_season").val();

    if (golfers < 13) {
      $("#total_cost").html("FREE");
      $("#cost_details").html("");
    } else {
      var cost = 0;
      var costPerGolfer = 0;

      if (tournaments > 15) {
        costPerGolfer = 10;
      } else {
        costPerGolfer = 5;
      }

      cost = golfers * costPerGolfer;

      $("#total_cost").html("$" + cost);
      $("#cost_details").html("($"+ costPerGolfer +" per golfer)");
    }
  }

  updateCalculatedCost();
</script>
